Description:
============
    Stubs out a new metric. Passes the metirc name, either CamelCased or
    under_scored, and an optional named arguments defining values.

    This generates a metric class in app/metrics.

Example:
========
    rails generate metricky:metric TotalUsers --scope User --period day --type count

    creates a Metricky metric class:
        Metric:     app/metrics/total_users_metric.rb